OK, team, listen up!

If you will pay me more,  than my current job -  I'll take the trouble
of enlightening you [and you, Ms. D], by opening your eyes to the nice
opportunities computer industry offers: you don't need to have a human 
listening to every line to get the info you want!Just put one computer 
somewhere close to the trunk, and scan the stream for the key-words... 
Those selected messages can now be reviewed by much smaller number of 
employees. This method was proven well by some agencies monitoring US 
and foreign cables.

May I get my payment in cash now? (:-)
